            <title>[PDFBOX-744] Landscape PDF Rasterized as Portrait</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-744</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Rotate entry on Page objects is not taken into account when converting a PDF into an image.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
